description = "Ace Combat: Assault Horizon Legacy is an action video game for the Nintendo 3DS, developed by Access Games and published by Namco Bandai Games and it is a remake of Ace Combat 2. Despite the game's international title outside Japan, it is not a direct sequel to the Ace Combat: Assault Horizon and has little relation to the game. The original Japanese version features compatibility with the Circle Pad Pro accessory."
